Russia’s Anisimov Plans to Sell Up to $4.7 Billion of Property, RBC Says

-- B y   I l y a   A r k h i p o v
-- 
2011-06-06T05:46:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-06/russia-s-anisimov-plans-to-sell-up-to-4-7-billion-of-property-rbc-says.html
Russian billionaire Vasily Anisimov,
co-owner of metals producer Metalloinvest, plans to sell his
real estate holdings for as much as $4.7 billion, RBC Daily
 reported , citing unidentified people familiar with the matter.  St. Petersburg-based LSR Group is interested in the Moscow
development’s of Anisimov’s Coalco Development property company,
the Moscow-based newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
